Django user accounts.


Documentation
-------------

@TODO: The full documentation is at https://django-guitar-accounts.readthedocs.io.


Quickstart
----------

Install Django Guitar Accounts::

    pip install django-guitar-accounts

Add it to your `INSTALLED_APPS`:

.. code-block:: python

    INSTALLED_APPS = (
        ...
        'guitar_accounts.apps.GuitarAccountsConfig',
        ...
    )

Add it to the `MIDDLEWARE` list, after `GuitarMiddleware`:

.. code-block:: python

    MIDDLEWARE = [
        ...
        "guitar.middlewares.GuitarMiddleware",
        "guitar_accounts.middlewares.UserMiddleware",
    ]


Add Django Guitar Accounts's URL patterns:

.. code-block:: python

    from guitar_accounts import urls as accounts_urls


    urlpatterns = [
        ...
        url(r'^accounts/', include(accounts_urls)),
        ...
    ]
